      An encouraging exposition on the current successes of traditional businesses shifting to the subscription model. The author himself espouses a system he devised called PADRE (pipeline, acquire, deploy, run, expand) to transform a business into a customer-oriented subscription service. I liked the nod to Agile initiated in software development practice. I was one of the many who despised Adobe's move for Creative Cloud but now in 2019, it's inevitably the future for most industries. And I believe that ultimately it's only going to be good for customers because of continuous product and service innovations.       ...more
